本頁面是2017年間古典音樂事件（含相關話題）的紀錄頁。

== 事件 ==
=== 1月 ===
* [[1月1日|1日]]：[[古斯塔沃·杜達美|古斯塔沃·杜達美]]指揮[[维也纳新年音乐会|维也纳新年音乐会]]之演出。這是他首次執棒維也納新年音樂會，他是該會歷史上最年輕的登台指揮者<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.br-klassik.de/aktuell/wiener-neujahrskonzert-100.html | title=Gustavo Dudamel dirigiert die Wiener Philharmoniker | work=BR-Klassik | author=Bettina Jech | date=2017-01-02 | accessdate=2017-01-12 | archive-date=2020-11-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128111223/https://www.br-klassik.de/aktuell/wiener-neujahrskonzert-100.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* [[1月3日|5日]]：[[丹麥皇家劇院|丹麥皇家劇院]]宣布與藝術總監Sven Müller{{譯名請求}}解約，其合約原本預計在2020年到期<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.dr.dk/nyheder/kultur/klassisk/det-kongelige-teaters-operachef-stopper-foer-tid | title=Det Kongelige Teaters operachef stopper før tid | work=DR (Danish Radio) | date=2017-01-05 | accessdate=2017-01-10 | archive-date=2019-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410184712/https://www.dr.dk/nyheder/kultur/klassisk/det-kongelige-teaters-operachef-stopper-foer-tid | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* [[1月10日|11日]]：{{link-en|新加坡交響樂團|Singapore Symphony Orchestra}}宣布，音樂總監{{link-en|水藍|Lan Shui}}將在2019年1月離任<ref>{{cite press release | url=https://www.sso.org.sg/media-release-detail.php?c=28&desc=Media+Releases&p=17511&t=lan-shui-to-step-down-as-ssos-music-director | title=Lan Shui to step down as SSO's Music Director | publisher=Singapore Symphony Orchestra | date=2017-01-11 | accessdate=2017-01-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113171139/https://www.sso.org.sg/media-release-detail.php?c=28&desc=Media+Releases&p=17511&t=lan-shui-to-step-down-as-ssos-music-director | archive-date=2017-01-13 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外，[[漢堡|漢堡]]的[[易北愛樂廳|易北愛樂廳]]落成後的第一場音樂會於今日舉行，由[[托马斯·亨格尔布洛克|托马斯·亨格尔布洛克]]指揮[[北德廣播易北愛樂樂團|北德廣播易北愛樂樂團]]及合唱團演出<ref name="Kettle">{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2017/jan/12/hamburg-elbphilharmonie-orchestra-hengelbrock-review-opening-concert | title=Elbphilharmonie Orchestra/Hengelbrock review – storming debut for hall of wonders | work=[[衛報|''The Guardian'']] | author=Martin Kettle | date=2017-01-12 | accessdate=2017-01-12 | archive-date=2020-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129212401/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2017/jan/12/hamburg-elbphilharmonie-orchestra-hengelbrock-review-opening-concert | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* [[1月17日|12日]]：[[倫敦市法團|倫敦地方政府]]宣布，將投入2,500,000英鎊經費進行新音樂廳建設的可行性評估計畫<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/jan/12/plan-for-world-class-concert-hall-in-city-of-london-back-on-track | title=Plan for world-class concert hall in City of London back on track | work=The Guardian | author=Mark Brown | date=2017-01-12 | accessdate=2017-01-20 | archive-date=2021-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303232402/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/jan/12/plan-for-world-class-concert-hall-in-city-of-london-back-on-track | dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個計畫曾在2016年11月暫時中止。
* [[1月23日|13日]]：[[黑森|黑森邦]]科學與藝術部門宣布，Francesco Angelico{{譯名請求}}將就任{{link-en|卡塞尔国立剧院|Staatstheater Kassel}}音樂總監，合約自2017年樂季起效<ref>{{cite press release | url=https://wissenschaft.hessen.de/presse/pressemitteilung/francesco-angelico-soll-neuer-generalmusikdirektor-am-hessischen-0 | title=Francesco Angelico soll neuer Generalmusikdirektor am Hessischen Staatstheater Kassel werden | publisher=Hessisches Ministerium für Wissenschaft und Kunst | date=2017-01-13 | accessdate=2017-04-22 | archive-date=2017-05-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518194734/https://wissenschaft.hessen.de/presse/pressemitteilung/francesco-angelico-soll-neuer-generalmusikdirektor-am-hessischen-0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* [[1月25日|18日]]：加州奧海音樂節宣布，[[帕特里恰·科帕钦斯卡亚|帕特里恰·科帕钦斯卡亚]]將在2018年擔任音樂節總監（取代了[[埃萨-佩卡·萨洛宁|埃萨-佩卡·萨洛宁]]，他因個人的作曲計畫而推辭了音樂節的任命）<ref>{{cite press release | url=http://www.ojaifestival.org/ojai-music-festival-updates-future-music-director-appointments/ | title=Ojai Festival Updates Future Music Directors: Patricia Kopatchinskaja to be Music Director in 2018 | publisher=Ojai Music Festival | date=2017-01-18 | accessdate=2017-01-28 }}{{Dead link|date=April 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。
* [[1月29日|20日]]：{{link-de|紐倫堡交響樂團|Nürnberger Symphoniker}}宣布新任首席指揮為{{link-en|黃佳俊|Wong Kah Chun}}，任期自2018年樂季起算<ref>{{cite press release | url=http://www.nuernbergersymphoniker.de/fileadmin/user_upload/presse_PDF/PM_Wong_200117.pdf | title=Kahchun Wong wird neuer Chefdirigent | publisher=Nuremberg Symphony Orchestra | date=2017-01-20 | accessdate=2017-01-24 | archive-date=2017-02-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202033450/http://www.nuernbergersymphoniker.de/fileadmin/user_upload/presse_PDF/PM_Wong_200117.pdf | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
* [[1月30日|22日]]：韓國女高音[[曹秀美|曹秀美]]在上海、廣州等地的演出遭到無預警取消。這一動作被認為是中华人民共和国政府對韓國[[薩德反飛彈系統|薩德反飛彈系統]]的回應<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/23/world/asia/sumi-jo-soprano-maria-callas.html | title=3 Performances by Sumi Jo, Korean Soprano, Canceled in China | work=[[纽约时报|''The New York Times'']] | author=Amy Qin | date=2017-01-23 | accessdate=2017-01-24 | archive-date=2021-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417160218/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/23/world/asia/sumi-jo-soprano-maria-callas.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 。（另參[[韓國部署薩德反導彈系統事件|韓國部署薩德反導彈系統事件]]）之後，鋼琴家[[白建宇|白建宇]]預計3月在貴陽的演出也告取消。
* [[1月30日|24日]]：[[纽约爱乐|纽约爱乐]]宣布，主席Matthew VanBesien{{譯名請求}}即將離任，他將轉往[[密歇根大学|密歇根大学]]任職<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/24/arts/music/new-york-philharmonic-president-to-step-down.html | title=New York Philharmonic President to Step Down | work=The New York Times | author=Michael Cooper | date=2017-01-24 | accessdate=2017-01-28 | archive-date=2021-05-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508102345/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/24/arts/music/new-york-philharmonic-president-to-step-down.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://arts.umich.edu/news-features/u-ms-university-musical-society-names-new-york-philharmonics-matthew-vanbesien-as-new-president/ | title=University Musical Society names New York Philharmonic's Matthew VanBesien as new president | publisher=University of Michigan | author=Sara Billman | date=2017-01-24 | accessdate=2017-01-28 | archive-date=2019-06-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615203229/https://arts.umich.edu/news-features/u-ms-university-musical-society-names-new-york-philharmonics-matthew-vanbesien-as-new-president/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* [[1月30日|25日]]：[[林肯中心室內樂協會|林肯中心室內樂協會]]{{link-en|斯托格獎|Stoeger Prize}}頒布，得主為[[:en:Huw_Watkins|:en:Huw Watkins]]<ref>{{cite press release | url=https://www.chambermusicsociety.org/about/news/huw-watkins-awarded-stoegger-prize/ | title=Huw Watkins Awarded Stoeger Prize | publisher=Chamber Music Society of Lincoln Center | date=2017-01-25 | accessdate=2017-02-01 | archive-date=2021-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302110151/https://www.chambermusicsociety.org/about/news/huw-watkins-awarded-stoegger-prize/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* [[1月30日|26日]]：鋼琴家[[皮埃尔-洛朗·艾马尔|皮埃尔-洛朗·艾马尔]]獲得[[恩斯特·冯·西门子音乐奖|西门子奖]]<ref>Ulrich Mosch, [http://www.evs-musikstiftung.ch/en/prize/prizes/prize-winner-2017/pierre-laurent-aimard.html 'Serving Music' (essay on the Ernst von Siemens Music Prize for 2017)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.evs-musikstiftung.ch/en/prize/prizes/prize-winner-2017/pierre-laurent-aimard.html |date=20201202134228 }}</ref>。多倫多{{tsl|en|Tafelmusik Baroque Orchestra|塔菲爾古樂團}}宣布Elisa Citterio{{譯名請求}}將任下任音樂總監，自2017年7月起效<ref>{{cite press release | url=http://www.tafelmusik.org/ElisaCitterioMediaRelease | title=Tafelmusik Names New Music Director: Violinist Elisa Citterio | publisher=Tafelmusik Baroque Orchestra and Chamber Choir | date=2017-01-26 | accessdate=2017-01-28 | archive-date=2019-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410184734/https://www.tafelmusik.org/ElisaCitterioMediaRelease | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
* [[1月30日|29日]]：[[柏林國立樂團|柏林國立樂團]]與[[丹尼尔·巴伦博伊姆|丹尼尔·巴伦博伊姆]]在紐約[[卡内基大厅|卡內基廳]]完成了[[安东·布鲁克纳|安东·布鲁克纳]]交響曲的全本演出，為美國境內首見<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/30/arts/music/bruckner-barenboim-staatskapelle-berlin-carnegie-hall.html | title=When a Composer Just Doesn't Do It for You (No Matter How Much You Listen) | work=The New York Times | author=Corinna da Fonseca-Wollheim and Zachary Woolfe | date=2017-01-30 | accessdate=2017-02-01 | archive-date=2019-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129013618/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/30/arts/music/bruckner-barenboim-staatskapelle-berlin-carnegie-hall.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。系列演出自1月19日開始，20日的音樂會則是巴伦博伊姆個人在卡內基廳的六十週年亮相紀念。

=== 2月 ===
* [[2月2日|2日]]：[[格拉茨歌剧院|格拉茨歌剧院]]宣布，[[奥克萨娜·利尼夫|奥克萨娜·利尼夫]]將自2017年樂季起擔任該院音樂總監，合約為三年期<ref>{{cite news | title=Oksana Lyniv wird neue Chefdirigentin der Grazer Oper | url=http://diepresse.com/home/kultur/klassik/5163783/Oksana-Lyniv-wird-neue-Chefdirigentin-der-Grazer-Oper | work=Die Presse | date=2017-02-02 | accessdate=2017-03-11 | archive-date=2018-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123065719/https://diepresse.com/home/kultur/klassik/5163783/Oksana-Lyniv-wird-neue-Chefdirigentin-der-Grazer-Oper | dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，波士顿交响乐团宣布，James Burton{{譯名請求}}將擔任檀格塢節慶合唱團、波士頓交響樂團附設合唱團指揮<ref>{{cite press release | url=https://www.bso.org/brands/bso/press/press-releases/archived-press-releases/122716/february-2-2017-james-burton.aspx | title=Boston Symphony and Andris Nelsons Announce Major Appointment in Music Leadership: James Burton is Appointed Conductor of the Tanglewood Festival Chorus and Also Takes on Newly Established Role of BSO Choral Director | publisher=Boston Symphony Orchestra | date=2017-02-02 | accessdate=2017-02-06 | archive-date=2017-03-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170315155954/https://www.bso.org/brands/bso/press/press-releases/archived-press-releases/122716/february-2-2017-james-burton.aspx | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
